title: issue with shared files after upgrade 5.0.9 to 5.0.13 community
body:
1) install oc5.0.9 community on ubuntu 
2) create 2 users 
3) user a has a file called lab.txt and a folder called "test" with 1 file in it 
4) user a shares lab.txt and test to user b 
5) copy oc5.0.13 community to server 
6) copy data and config directories from oc5.0.9 instance to the new oc5.0.13 directory 
7) modify config.php to point to the new directory for oc5.0.13 
8) log in as user b 
    shared directory exists 
        lab.txt was visable 
        test was visable 
        click on test -- takes me back to "shared" directory -- did not see the file in test directory 
        click on lab.txt -- logged me out of oc with error 
9) log in as user a 
       neither the file nor folder had the "shared" tag enabled
